title: Lick Library -  Play - Easy Acoustic Rock 2
description: Celebrated Tutor Jamie Humphries Continues His Beginners' Guide To The Best Of Acoustic Rock Guitar-Playing. Humphries Presents Eight Proven Rock Classics That Are Particularly Suited To The Acoustic Guitar. This Terrific Lesson DVD Contains Note-For-Note Tutorials And Visual Aids That Will Get You Playing Such Unstoppable Songs As The Man Who Sold The World, Californication And Fake Plastic Trees Straight Away. The Disc Features Songs By Coldplay, David Gray And More.
